snippet.textDisplay: If you watch CS Pak, this would sound as noise pollution....we don't play to our strengths....we have such rich classical and regional talent but we still have to get western tone to something which could have sounded so much soothing if kept simple. This is a khichdi cooked by a confused chef with putting in some unnecessary ingredients......we are not good western singers....time we acknowledge that and play to our strengths.Mame khan pieces in the song sound so good while Mili Nari spoiled it
